(n=10; 
Figs. 12–21
). Reddish green to pale red in color. Length of body including gnathosoma 310–350; width of body 170–190.

Dorsum. Dorsal body setae stout, strong, longer than distance between bases of consecutive setae, length of setae: v 2 45–55; sc 1 73–122; sc 2 65–95; c 1 85–125; c 2 80–120; c 3 60–87; d 1 78–117; d 2 75–115;
